ActBudget Implementation Act, 2000
PrecisOrder Amending the SCHEDULE to the BUDGET IMPLEMENTATION ACT, 2000 (LITTLE SHUSWAP LAKE) by adding the name of this First Nation to the list of Indian Bands whose Councils may make by-laws imposing a direct tax on alcoholic beverages, fuel or tobacco products.
